sentences: Kernal "Kitch" Roberts (born Kernel Lincoln Roberts, 20 September 1980) is a soca producer, singer and songwriter from Trinidad and Tobago.
He is best known for producing Trinidad and Tobago Carnival Road March winners in 2006, 2007, 2010 and 2011.
